ai_brain = Sequential([
  Dense(6,input_shape=(8,)),
  Dense(10,activation='relu'),
  Dense(10,activation='relu'),
  Dense(4,activation='softmax'),
])

    
 
 

        

          

          

            
 

          

        

      

        
          add
          Code
        
        
          add
          Text
        
        
      

    

      

        

          
          

            
          

        

      
ai_brain.compile(optimizer='adam',
                 loss='categorical_crossentropy',
                 metrics=['accuracy'])

             validation_data=(X_test_scaled,y_test),
             )
